headline: CHAI: $48M/Year in Revenue After Funding Round by AMD and CoreWeave
summary: CHAI, the fast-rising social AI platform redefining human–AI interaction, has surpassed its 2025 revenue target two months ahead of schedule, reaching $48 million by the end of October. The company now projects over $50 million in annual recurring revenue (ARR) by year's end, representing an extraordinary 2.5x increase from $20 million at the beginning of 2025.
